- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with linguistic writing style analysis. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper discusses signature recognition. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with authorship attribution. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is relevant as the paper has applications in judicial and police-related documents analysis. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a machine learning-based approach for the multi-biometric system.
